{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10109402762122-1":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10109402762122-1","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":null,"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100130082472-1","P_10100130082472-2","P_10100130082472-3","P_10100130082472-4","P_10100130082472-5","P_10100130082472-6"],"books":null,"booksNew":[{"seriesId":"BKC_10100000002119","bookId":"BK_10100000007851","unitId":null,"lessonId":null,"sectionId":null,"termType":1,"classLevel":5}],"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":5,"description":"阅读文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":480,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>成全善良</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">​那是三月里的一天，我去医院看望一个生病的朋友。 </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">​因为是双休日，等公交车的人很多，在我旁边站着一个老人和他的女儿，听他们的对话，是陪老人去医院看病的，正好跟我同路。 </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">​那个女儿为了不让人群碰撞到父亲，一手在前面挡着人群，一手搀着父亲的胳膊上车。车上早就人满为患，这时一个姑娘战了起来，微笑着对那位老人说：“大爷，您来这里坐吧！”可那位老人却说：“谢谢了，姑娘，我站站没关系，你坐吧！”那女儿也说父亲身体硬朗着，站站就到了！ </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">​那个姑娘似乎没想到会这样，有些尴尬，再次说：“您坐吧，大爷！”那个女儿似乎还想说什么，只见老人拉了拉她的手，说：“好好，那就太谢谢你了！”说完，慢慢走到座位前微笑着坐下，那位姑娘流露出笑意。但我发现那个女儿明显不高兴，好像责怪父亲似的。让我看得很疑惑。 </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">​公交车开始加速，突然一下子急刹车，我注意到，那位老人紧皱着眉头，好像在强忍着身体某处的不适。我不禁替他暗自庆幸：亏他坐下了，如果一直站着，不知要遭多少罪。 </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">​医院很快就到了。那位老人下车时，不忘向那位姑娘表示感谢。我也下了车，拿出手机准备给朋友打电话，问清他在哪个病室。也正因为我这样停了一停，我才听到了下面这段对话： </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">​“爸，伤口痛了吧？” “一点点吧！” </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">​“你也真是的，明明知道自己臀部有伤口，不能坐，还要坐！” </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">​“人家小姑娘一片好意！我硬是拒绝她，也许以后再遇到这样的事，她就会有顾虑了......” </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">​我终于明白了，老人和他女儿的拒绝，原来并非客套。我不禁又想起车上的老人紧皱眉头的表情，在那颠簸的公交车上，老人硬是强忍着原本可以避免的痛楚，成全那个姑娘的善良。 </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">​成全别人的善良，又何尝不是另一种善良！</span></p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"这个故事告诉我们什么道理？","answers":[{"answer":"3","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":null,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"other","options":[{"option":"公交车上要主动让座，要乐于接受别人的好意。","file":null},{"option":"评价别人不能看表面，要看内在。","file":null},{"option":"朋友病了要去医院探望。","file":null},{"option":"成全别人的善良，也是一种善良。","file":null}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101007],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]},{"content":"作者是如何一步步知道事情的真相的？","answers":[{"answer":"3","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":null,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"other","options":[{"option":"通过询问老人的女儿。","file":null},{"option":"通过跟踪老人和女儿以及偷听他们的对话。","file":null},{"option":"通过医院朋友的介绍。","file":null},